《聽我吼》於多間錄音室進行錄音，其中包括位於[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的回放錄音室以及秘密花園錄音室，以及盧克博士的錄音室。此外歌曲亦在位於[[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]的{{tsl|en|MXM Studios||MXM錄音室}}進行錄音。歌曲派瑞與邦尼·麥基以及歌曲的製作人盧克博士、馬克斯·馬丁與西庫特共同創作。<ref name="Notes">{{cite AV media notes |title=Prism |titlelink=Prism (Katy Perry album) |others=[[凱蒂·佩芮|凱蒂·佩芮]] |year=2013 |type=liner notes |publisher=[[國會音樂集團|國會]] |location=[[美国|美国]]}}</ref>整個過程皆於2013年3月完成進行<ref name=KatyOnPrism>{{cite web |last=Perry |first=Katy |title=Katy Perry - Prism |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dCIVlrUWMn8 |publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2013-11-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106164914/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dCIVlrUWMn8 |archivedate=2014-01-06 }}</ref>。麥基在接受[[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]]訪問時稱《聽我吼》是「有關重拾自我、抹掉身上灰塵繼續前行」、「女性主權歌曲」以及「有所頓悟的歌曲」<ref>{{cite web |author=Vena, Jocelyn |title=Go Behind Katy Perry's 'Raw And Emotional' Prism Writing Sessions |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1716064/katy-perry-bonnie-mckee-prism.jhtml |publisher=[[音樂電視網|MTV]] |accessdate=2013-12-23 |date=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205010633/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1716064/katy-perry-bonnie-mckee-prism.jhtml |archivedate=2013-12-05 }}</ref>。派瑞提及歌曲說在自己接受輔導後創作，指自己「對把這些感覺埋藏心底而未有為自己發聲感到厭倦」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbs.com/shows/grammys/news/1001829/behind-the-56th-grammy-awards-song-of-the-year-nominees/ |title=Behind The 56th GRAMMY Awards: Song Of The Year Nominees |publisher=CBS |accessdate=2016-08-30 |date=2014-01-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918134157/http://www.cbs.com/shows/grammys/news/1001829/behind-the-56th-grammy-awards-song-of-the-year-nominees/ |archivedate=2016-09-18 }}</ref>。

在音樂性上，《聽我吼》是一首具有{{tsl|en|arena rock||舞台搖滾}}風格的[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行歌曲]]<ref>{{cite journal |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/on-the-charts-katy-perry-and-lady-gaga-singles-duke-it-out-20130821 |title=On the Charts: Katy Perry and Lady Gaga Singles Duke It Out |first=Steve |last=Knopper |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |date=2013-08-21 |accessdate=2016-08-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911050626/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/on-the-charts-katy-perry-and-lady-gaga-singles-duke-it-out-20130821 |archivedate=2016-09-11 |journal= }}</ref><ref name="Slate1">{{cite web |url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2013/08/12/katy_perry_new_single_roar_latest_song_is_a_jock_jams_pastiche.html |title=Katy Perry new single "Roar": Latest song is a Jock Jams pastiche |first=Forrest |last=Wickman |work={{tsl|en|Slate (magazine)||Slate}} |date=2013-08-12 |accessdate=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812194011/http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2013/08/12/katy_perry_new_single_roar_latest_song_is_a_jock_jams_pastiche.html |archivedate=2013-08-12 }}</ref>。其中歌詞受到{{le|海倫·雷迪|Helen Reddy}}1971年的歌曲經典歌詞「我是女人，聽我吼」啟發<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.radio.com/2014/01/02/behind-the-song-katy-perrys-roar/ |title=Behind the Song: Katy Perry’s ‘Roar’ |publisher=Radio |accessdate=2017-10-15 |date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311203429/http://news.radio.com/2014/01/02/behind-the-song-katy-perrys-roar/ |archive-date=2014-03-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。歌曲的{{tsl|en|instrumentation||伴奏}}由「重拍」的鋼琴聲以及「低沉回響」的低音鼓聲組成<ref name="rollingstone1">{{cite web |first=Caryn |last=Ganz |title=Katy Perry - "Roar" |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/songreviews/roar-20130828 |work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] |accessdate=2013-12-23 |date=2013-08-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024073826/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/songreviews/roar-20130828 |archivedate=2013-10-24 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》以[[降B大調|降B大調]]創作，是一首中等[[速度_(音樂)|速度]]的[[拍號|4/4拍]]歌曲，每分鐘達90[[速度_(音樂)|拍]]。派瑞在歌曲的[[音域|音域]]範圍由最低B{{music|flat}}<sub>3</sub>到最高E{{music|flat}}<sub>5</sub>，而音樂的{{tsl|en|chord progression||和弦進程}}則為B{{music|flat}}–Cm–Gm–E{{music|flat}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry "Roar" Sheet Music - Download & Print|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtdFPE.asp?ppn=MN0122655&ref=google|publisher=Musicnotes.com|accessdate=2013-12-23}}</ref>。歌曲在主題上有著與過往作品《[[煙火_(歌曲)|煙火]]》相似的勵志主題<ref name="Vibe">{{cite web |last=Rogulewski |first=Charley |title=Katy Perry's New Single "Roar" Leaks |url=http://www.vibe.com/article/katy-perry-roar |work=Vibe magazine |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812232434/http://www.vibe.com/article/katy-perry-roar |archivedate=2013-08-12 }}</ref><ref name="EnterntainmentWeeklyReview">{{cite web |last=Atkinson |first=Katie |title=Katy Perry is back with a 'Roar' — hear her new single now |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/08/11/katy-perry-roar-single-listen/ |work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2013-08-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814003016/http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/08/11/katy-perry-roar-single-listen/ |archivedate=2013-08-14 |accessdate=2017-10-15 }}</ref>。派瑞形容歌曲為一首關於為自己加油的歌<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1713155/katy-perry-roar-biggest-bully.jhtml |first=Christina |last=Garibaldi |publisher=MTV |title=Katy Perry Used To Be Her 'Biggest Bully' Before 'Roar' |date=2013-08-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130830021759/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1713155/katy-perry-roar-biggest-bully.jhtml |archivedate=2013-08-30 |accessdate=2017-10-15 }}</ref>。

