《[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]》的史蒂芬·托馬斯·艾爾維恩讚賞歌曲的成熟性，並認為派瑞藉此擺脫以往的甜心形象<ref name=allmusic>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/prism-mw0002577862 |title=''Prism''— Katy Perry |first=Stephen Thomas |last=Erlewine |publisher=AllMusic. All Media Network |date=2013-10-21 |accessdate=2017-10-16 |archive-date=2013-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024001157/http://www.allmusic.com/album/prism-mw0002577862 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的米麗安·科爾曼讚揚歌曲的「簡單的流行節奏」以及它「重覆的副歌」，並讓她認為歌曲製定了專輯的基調<ref name="RollingStone2">{{cite web |last=Coleman |first=Miriam |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-drops-new-song-roar-20130811 |title=Katy Perry Drops New Song, 'Roar' |work=Rolling Stone |date=2013-08-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812112437/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-drops-new-song-roar-20130811 |archivedate=2013-08-12 |accessdate=2017-10-16 }}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的格里克·迪·肯尼迪同樣給予歌曲正面的評價，把歌曲比喻為被咬了一口的甜點<ref name="Angeles">{{cite news |last=Kennedy |first=Gerrick D. |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-listen-to-katy-perry-roar-20130811,0,3722661.story |title=Listen to Katy Perry's new single 'Roar' |newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2013-08-11 |accessdate=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812125251/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-listen-to-katy-perry-roar-20130811%2C0%2C3722661.story |archivedate=2013-08-12 }}</ref><ref name="MTV2">{{cite web |last=Montgomery |first=James |title=Katy Perry's 'Roar:' The Power Of Positive Thinking |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1712162/katy-perry-roar-release.jhtml |publisher=MTV News |accessdate=2013-08-12 |date=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815053720/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1712162/katy-perry-roar-release.jhtml |archivedate=2013-08-15 }}</ref>。《前音後果》的克里斯·博斯曼讚賞歌曲的副歌讓人無論在任何情況都能高聲唱出來，並指這已成為青少年的頌歌<ref name=consequence>{{cite web |url=http://consequenceofsound.net/2013/10/album-review-katy-perry-prism/ |title=Album Review: Katy Perry – Prism |publisher=Consequence of Sound |date=2013-10-21 |accessdate=2014-01-05 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021053418/http://consequenceofsound.net/2013/10/album-review-katy-perry-prism/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[Hitfix|Hitfix]]》的梅琳達·紐曼認為派瑞在歌曲裡「改變了步伐」<ref>{{cite web |last=Newman |first=Melinda |url=http://www.hitfix.com/news/katy-perrys-new-single-roar-in-full-is-a-fierce-fun-anthem-listen |title=Listen: Katy Perry's new single Roar in full, is a fierce, fun anthem |publisher=Hitfix.com |date=2013-06-25 |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813043029/http://www.hitfix.com/news/katy-perrys-new-single-roar-in-full-is-a-fierce-fun-anthem-listen |archivedate=2013-08-13 }}</ref>，而《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》的德魯·漢普普則認為歌曲回到她過往的專輯《[[花漾派對|花漾派對]]》裡的風格，但對歌曲的節奏以及歌詞作出批評，最終於滿分5星給予歌曲4星的評價<ref name="Track">{{cite web |last=Hampp |first=Andrew |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/5645969/katy-perry-roar-track-review |title=Katy Perry, 'Roar: Track Review |publisher=''Billboard''. [[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]] |date=2013-08-12 |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814235701/http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/5645969/katy-perry-roar-track-review |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref>。《[[偏鋒雜誌|偏鋒雜誌]]》的薩爾·辛坤馬尼認為歌曲雖然比起吼叫更像是在尖叫，但的確展示了她的成長<ref name=slant>{{cite web|last=Cinquemani|first=Sal|url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/katy-perry-prism|title=Katy Perry: Prism|work=Slant Magazine|date=2013-10-18|accessdate=2017-10-16|archive-date=2013-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018021609/http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/katy-perry-prism|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===爭議===
《聽我吼》發行前後，派瑞被多方指責歌曲涉嫌抄襲[[莎拉·芭瑞黎絲|莎拉·芭瑞黎絲]]的歌曲《[[Brave_(莎拉·芭瑞黎絲歌曲)|勇敢]]》<ref name="Angeles"/><ref name="MusicMix">{{cite web |last=Anderson |first=Kyle |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/08/12/katy-perry-roar-sara-bareilles-brave/ |title=Katy Perry's 'Roar' sounds an awful lot like Sara Bareilles' 'Brave', says the Internet |work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2013-08-12 |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813013816/http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/08/12/katy-perry-roar-sara-bareilles-brave/ |archivedate=2013-08-13 }}</ref><ref name="Brave-ly Roar">{{cite web |last=Pavlova |first=Victoria |title=Katy Perry And Sara Bareilles "Brave"-ly "Roar" In The Face Of Plagiarism Speculation |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/article/katy-perry-roar-sara-bareilles-brave-similarity_3810877 |publisher=Contactmusic.com |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814112829/http://www.contactmusic.com/article/katy-perry-roar-sara-bareilles-brave-similarity_3810877 |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref><ref name="Global News">{{cite web |last=Kennedy |first=John R. |title=Katy Perry accused of being copy cat |url=http://globalnews.ca/news/778353/katy-perry-accused-of-being-copy-cat/ |publisher=Global News |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815061329/http://globalnews.ca/news/778353/katy-perry-accused-of-being-copy-cat/ |archivedate=2013-08-15 }}</ref>。當芭瑞黎絲被問到關於歌曲間的抄襲風波時，她回應：「派瑞是我的朋友，我們已經相識了一段長時間」，並對「從負面的角度去對待兩位歌手傳遞正面的信息」感到難過。她亦提及自己在《聽我吼》發行前已經知道這首歌，並指：「連我自己也沒為此生氣，不明白其他人在難過甚麼。<ref name="Bareilles ABC">{{cite web |title=Sara Bareilles on 'Brave' vs. Katy Perry's 'Roar' |url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2013/08/sara-bareilles-on-brave-vs-katy-perrys-roar/ |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=2013-08-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901044247/http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2013/08/sara-bareilles-on-brave-vs-katy-perrys-roar/ |archivedate=2013-09-01 }}</ref>」對於抄襲指控，[[卢克博士|卢克博士]]於2013年8月14日在推特發表回應：「《聽我吼》在《勇敢》發行前便已經寫好並完成錄製<ref>{{cite web |title=too bad..... |url=https://twitter.com/TheDoctorLuke/statuses/367577095125204993 |publisher="[[Twitter|Twitter]]" |accessdate=2013-09-14 |date=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921230348/https://twitter.com/TheDoctorLuke/statuses/367577095125204993 |archivedate=2013-09-21 }}</ref>。」對於《勇敢》在抄襲風波再次獲得大眾關注，芭瑞黎絲的唱片公司[[史诗唱片|史诗唱片]]其後順勢重新把歌曲派往[[當代流行電台|主流流行電台]]播放<ref>{{cite web |last=Trust |first=Gary |title=Weekly Chart Notes: The 27 Songs To Spend At Least 10 Weeks Atop The Hot 100 |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5657724/weekly-chart-notes-the-27-songs-to-spend-at-least-10-weeks-atop-the-hot-100 |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2013-08-16 |accessdate=2013-08-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827063735/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5657724/weekly-chart-notes-the-27-songs-to-spend-at-least-10-weeks-atop-the-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-08-27 }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
派瑞透過一段燒毀藍色假髮的預告片段宣佈《聽我吼》成為專輯《超炫光》的首支發行單曲<ref>{{cite web |title=Katy Perry Will 'Roar' Back Fiery New Track: Watch Her Tease! |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1711741/katy-perry-roar-new-single/ |publisher=MTV News |first=Jocelyn |last=Vena |accessdate=2016-08-30 |date=2013-08-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911110307/http://www.mtv.com/news/1711741/katy-perry-roar-new-single/ |archivedate=2016-09-11 }}</ref>。其後派瑞於[[YouTube|YouTube]]上傳更多歌曲預告片段，包括展示派瑞出席葬禮的片段，而片段則出現以她標誌性的粉白風車裙裝飾的棺材<ref name="bill">{{cite web |date=2013-08-06 |accessdate=2013-12-01 |title=Katy Perry Buries Alter-Ego In New Teaser Clip |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/katy-perry/387796-katy-perry-roar-second-teaser-the-third-coming-prism#3ChMSJcTbyzet0i0.99 |publisher=[[音樂電視網|MTV]] |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204024149/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/katy-perry/387796-katy-perry-roar-second-teaser-the-third-coming-prism#3ChMSJcTbyzet0i0.99 |archivedate=2013-12-04 }}</ref>，而另一於2013年8月8日公開的片段則展現了派瑞穿著與單曲封面相同的外套進入錄音棚的模樣<ref name="Williott">{{cite web |last=Williott |first=Carl |title=Katy Perry Rocks "Roar" Jacket In Latest Teaser: Hear Another Snippet Of The Song |url=http://www.idolator.com/7476606/katy-perry-roar-teaser-snippet-jacket |website={{tsl|en|Idolator (website)|Idolator (網站)|Idolator}} |date=2013-08-09 |accessdate=2013-12-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203022359/http://www.idolator.com/7476606/katy-perry-roar-teaser-snippet-jacket |archivedate=2013-12-03 }}</ref><ref name="Williott"/> 單曲封面以派瑞穿著背面繡著老虎圖案的橫須賀刺繡外套為主，並在外框同樣加上老虎的花紋圖案<ref name="style">{{cite web |title=Katy Perry's 'Roar' Single Cover Style Is Very Lisa Frank Meets 'Drive' |url=http://style.mtv.com/2013/08/08/katy-perry-roar-cover/ |last=Keirans |first=Maeve |publisher=[[音樂電視網|MTV]] |accessdate=2013-08-08 |date=2013-08-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813123417/http://style.mtv.com/2013/08/08/katy-perry-roar-cover |archivedate=2013-08-13 }}</ref>。在歌曲數位發行當天，歌曲的歌詞版音樂錄像帶亦同時於YouTube公開。整个歌词版音乐录像带以应用程式[[WhatsApp|WhatsApp]]为背景，以佩芮使用[[iPhone|iPhone]]向其它人传送讯息叙述佩芮的日常生活。其中部分文字会以[[繪文字|繪文字]]代替<ref name="Video">{{cite web |last=Moraski |first=Lauren |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57598116/watch-katy-perrys-emoticon-lyric-video-for-roar/ |title=Watch: Katy Perry's emoticon lyric video for "Roar" |publisher=CBS News |date=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812175316/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57598116/watch-katy-perrys-emoticon-lyric-video-for-roar/ |archivedate=2013-08-12 |accessdate=2017-10-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Mallenbaum |first=Carly |title=Katy Perry releases 'emoticon' video for 'Roar' |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2013/08/12/katy-perry-roar-emoticon/2642249/ |work=[[今日美國|USA Today]] |accessdate=2013-08-12 |date=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815063522/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2013/08/12/katy-perry-roar-emoticon/2642249/ |archivedate=2013-08-15 }}</ref>。錄像帶其後引起音樂製作人{{tsl|en|Dillon Francis||狄龍·法蘭西斯}}的抄襲疑慮，認為錄像帶抄襲了自己的作品《訊息》的音樂錄像帶概念<ref name="Copy">{{cite web |last=Reilly |first=Dan |title=Dillon Francis Says Katy Perry's 'Roar' Ripped Him Off, But She'll Play the VMAs Anyway |url=http://www.spin.com/articles/katy-perry-rip-off-dillon-francis-roar-video-vmas/ |work=[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]] |accessdate=2013-08-12 |date=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814135653/http://www.spin.com/articles/katy-perry-rip-off-dillon-francis-roar-video-vmas/ |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref>。

歌曲的首支預告片段於2013年8月2日公開，並同時宣佈歌曲會在8月12日於美國發行<ref>{{cite journal |title=Katy Perry Posts 'Roar' Teaser, Announces Single Release Date |journal=Billboard |accessdate=2014-03-01 |date=2013-08-02 |last=Gocobachi |first=Pam |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5638070/katy-perry-posts-roar-teaser-announces-single-release-date |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221105816/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5638070/katy-perry-posts-roar-teaser-announces-single-release-date |archivedate=2014-02-21 }}</ref>以及於8月13日被送往[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]派台<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vU77yxmZ?url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases |archivedate=2011-01-04 |title=Top 40/M Future Releases |publisher=All Access Music Group |accessdate=2017-10-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而歌曲於正式發行前兩天的8月10日遭到提前泄露而決定提前於當天正式派台<ref name="radio">{{cite web |date=2013-08-10 |title=Katy Perry's New Single 'Roar' Leaks: Listen |url=http://news.radio.com/2013/08/10/katy-perry-roar-leak/ |first=Courtney E. |last=Smith |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310083408/http://news.radio.com/2013/08/10/katy-perry-roar-leak/ |archivedate=2014-03-10 |df= |accessdate=2017-10-15 }}</ref>。歌曲原本計劃於9月8日在英國發行，但派瑞於8月30日宣佈歌曲提前於9月1日發行<ref name="0901MTV">{{cite web |title=Katy Perry Brings Roar's UK Release Date Forward |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/katy-perry/news/katy-perry-brings-roars-uk-release-date-forward |date=2013-08-30 |accessdate=2014-03-01 |publisher=MTV |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310091101/http://www.mtv.co.uk/katy-perry/news/katy-perry-brings-roars-uk-release-date-forward |archivedate=2014-03-10 }}</ref>。

==商業成績==
===北美地區===
歌曲於正式發行前一週憑藉電台播放而提前空降[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]第85位<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5650672/robin-thicke-leads-hot-100-for-10th-week-katy-perrys-roar-debuts |work=Billboard |title=Robin Thicke Leads Hot 100 For 10th Week, Katy Perry's 'Roar' Debuts |first=Gary |last=Trust |date=2013-08-14 |accessdate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816033503/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5650672/robin-thicke-leads-hot-100-for-10th-week-katy-perrys-roar-debuts |archivedate=2013-08-16 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》於正式發行首週售出557,000首下載量，成為2013年美國最高首週銷量的歌曲，並打破派瑞另一首單曲《[[煙火_(歌曲)|煙火]]》於2011年單週售出509,000首的紀錄，成為其本人最高單週銷量的單曲<ref name="roar">{{cite news |first=Keith |last=Caulfield |title=Luke Bryan Nets No. 1 Album, Katy Perry's 'Roar' Tops Digital Songs |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5659205/luke-bryan-nets-no-1-album-katy-perrys-roar-tops-digital-songs |work=Billboard |date=2013-08-21 |accessdate=2013-08-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821153153/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5659205/luke-bryan-nets-no-1-album-katy-perrys-roar-tops-digital-songs |archivedate=2013-08-21 }}</ref>。歌曲於進榜次週躍升83位至第2位，僅次於[[罗宾·西克|罗宾·西克]]的《[[模糊界線|模糊界線]]》，同時成為派瑞於美國第12首打進前10位的單曲，以及其連續第9首打進前3位的單曲<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5660927/robin-thicke-no-1-katy-perry-no-2-on-hot-100 |work=Billboard |title=Robin Thicke No. 1, Katy Perry No. 2 On Hot 100 |first=Gary |last=Trust |date=2013-08-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821172152/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5660927/robin-thicke-no-1-katy-perry-no-2-on-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-08-21 |accessdate=2017-10-14 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》連續兩週排行第2位後，於進榜第四週成功登上單曲榜冠軍位置，成為派瑞第8首於《告示牌》百強單曲榜的冠軍單曲，並同時憑448,000首的下載量成為其於[[公告牌数字歌曲榜|《告示牌》數字歌曲榜]]的第9首冠軍單曲<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680131/katy-perry-dethrones-robin-thicke-atop-hot-100 |work=Billboard |title=Katy Perry Dethrones Robin Thicke Atop Hot 100 |first=Gary |last=Trust |date=2013-09-04 |accessdate=2013-12-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906163801/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680131/katy-perry-dethrones-robin-thicke-atop-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-09-06 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》於冠軍位置逗留兩週後被[[麥莉·希拉|麥莉·希拉]]的《[[愛情破壞球|愛情破壞球]]》取代<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5695590/miley-cyrus-wrecking-ball-swings-to-top-of-hot-100 |work=Billboard |title=Miley Cyrus' 'Wrecking Ball' Swings Atop Hot 100 |first=Gary |last=Trust |date=2013-09-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920000156/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5695590/miley-cyrus-wrecking-ball-swings-to-top-of-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-09-20 |accessdate=2017-10-14 }}</ref>。歌曲於進榜第七週於[[公告牌百强电台歌曲榜|《告示牌》百強電台歌曲榜]]從以159萬電台聽眾的成績從亞軍升至冠軍位置，成為派瑞於該榜第6首冠軍單曲，也成為她於該榜最快奪冠的單曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5733088/miley-cyrus-wrecking-ball-spends-second-week-atop-hot-100 |title=Miley Cyrus' 'Wrecking Ball' Spends Second Week Atop Hot 100 |date=2013-09-25 |work=Billboard |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925202218/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5733088/miley-cyrus-wrecking-ball-spends-second-week-atop-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-09-25 |accessdate=2017-10-14 }}</ref>。

《聽我吼》亦登上了美國[[主流四十強單曲榜|主流四十強單曲榜]]與{{le|成人流行歌曲榜|Adult Pop Songs}}冠軍位置。其中歌曲成為派瑞於[[主流四十強單曲榜|流行歌曲]]榜的第10首冠軍歌曲，與[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]共享最多該榜冠軍單曲的紀錄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5695476/katy-perry-ties-for-most-pop-songs-no-1s |title=Katy Perry Ties For Most Pop Songs No. 1s |accessdate=2013-09-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918173552/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5695476/katy-perry-ties-for-most-pop-songs-no-1s |archivedate=2013-09-18 }}</ref>。而歌曲於成人流行歌曲榜奪冠後亦為派瑞帶來不少榮譽；歌曲成為派瑞於該榜的第8首冠軍單曲，與[[魔力紅|魔力紅]]與[[粉红佳人|粉红佳人]]共享最多該榜冠軍單曲的紀錄。歌曲亦打破其本人於2011年的單曲《[[加州女孩|加州女孩]]》最快登上冠軍位置的紀錄<ref name="Britney"/>。歌曲亦同時打破兩榜的單週電台播放紀錄，分別於單週播出16,065次以及5,309次<ref name=BillboardPDF>{{cite web |last=Trust |first=Gary |title=Miley Cyrus, Paramore Reach Top 10; Lorde Leaps To History |url=http://www1.billboard.biz/bbbiz/photos/pdf/2013/TFMm1007.pdf |work=Billboard |accessdate=2013-10-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019152413/http://www1.billboard.biz/bbbiz/photos/pdf/2013/TFMm1007.pdf |archivedate=2013-10-19 }}</ref>。

歌曲亦同時登上{{le|《告示牌》當代成人單曲榜|Adult Contemporary (chart)}}以及[[告示牌舞曲夜店歌曲榜|《告示牌》舞曲夜店歌曲榜]]冠軍位置<ref name="Britney">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5719511/chart-highlights-britney-spears-bows-katy-perry-lady-gaga-leap-to-no-1 |title=Britney Spears Bows, Katy Perry, Lady Gaga Leap To No. 1 |last=Trust |first=Gary |date=2013-09-23 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |work=Billboard |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925051118/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5719511/chart-highlights-britney-spears-bows-katy-perry-lady-gaga-leap-to-no-1 |archivedate=2013-09-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www1.billboard.biz/bbbiz/photos/pdf/2013/TFMm0923.pdf |title=Spears’ ‘Work’ Is Just Beginning; Perry, Drake Score New No. 1s |last=Trust |first=Gary |date=2013-09-23 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |work=Billboard |format=PDF |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927213630/http://www1.billboard.biz/bbbiz/photos/pdf/2013/TFMm0923.pdf |archivedate=2013-09-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/5762990/diplo-paris-hilton-lady-gaga-debut-on-dance-charts |title=Diplo, Paris Hilton, Lady Gaga Debut On Dance Charts |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2013-10-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ko1R07KA?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/5762990/diplo-paris-hilton-lady-gaga-debut-on-dance-charts |archivedate=2016-09-26 |accessdate=2017-10-14 }}</ref>。此外，歌曲亦同時以最高210萬點播次數以及1200萬流媒播放次數分別登上{{tsl|en|On-Demand Songs||電台點播榜}}與{{tsl|en|Streaming Songs||流媒體歌曲榜}}的冠軍位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680131/katy-perry-dethrones-robin-thicke-atop-hot-100 |title=Katy Perry Dethrones Robin Thicke Atop Hot 10 |work=Billboard |accessdate=2013-12-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906163801/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680131/katy-perry-dethrones-robin-thicke-atop-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-09-06 }}</ref><ref name="streaming">{{Cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5687387/katy-perrys-roar-rules-hot-100-for-second-week-lorde-reaches-top-3 |work=Billboard |title=Katy Perry's 'Roar' Rules Hot 100 For Second Week, Lorde Reaches Top 3 |first=Gary |last=Trust |date=2013-09-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130913203748/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5687387/katy-perrys-roar-rules-hot-100-for-second-week-lorde-reaches-top-3 |archivedate=2013-09-13 |accessdate=2017-10-14 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》於發行第17週突破400萬次下載量，成為有史以來最快的紀錄。歌曲於2013年年底達到441萬首下載量，成為該年第6高下載量的單曲。派瑞憑歌曲獲得第7首銷量突破400萬的單曲，成為歌手之冠<ref>{{cite web |last=Grein |first=Paul |title=Chart Watch: "The Monster" Lives Up To Its Title |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/chart-watch-monster-lives-title-013939655.html |publisher=Yahoo! |accessdate=2013-12-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216154718/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/chart-watch-monster-lives-title-013939655.html |archivedate=2013-12-16 }}</ref><ref name="sales 2013">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5855151/justin-timberlakes-2020-2013s-best-selling-album-blurred-lines-top-song |title=Justin Timberlake's '20/20' 2013's Best Selling Album, 'Blurred Lines' Top Song |first=Keith |last=Caulfield |work=Billboard |date=2014-01-02 |accessdate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105134039/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5855151/justin-timberlakes-2020-2013s-best-selling-album-blurred-lines-top-song |archivedate=2014-01-05 }}</ref>。截至2017年2月，歌曲於美國售出6,400,000首，並獲[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]認證為鑽石唱片，使派瑞成為史上首位於美國擁有3首鑽石單曲的歌手<ref name=USsales2017/>。

《聽我吼》於發行首週憑藉高下載量空降[[加拿大百强单曲榜|加拿大百强单曲榜]]冠軍位置<ref name="canada">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-08-31/canadian-hot-100 |title=Canadian Hot 100: August 31, 2013 |work=Billboard |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2013-08-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140608192242/http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-08-31/canadian-hot-100 |archivedate=2014-06-08 }}</ref>。這成為該榜史上第17首空降冠軍的單曲，也是派瑞第3首空降冠軍的單曲，使她成為於當地擁有最多空降冠軍單曲的歌手<ref name="canada" />。歌曲亦同時成為派瑞於該榜第9首冠軍單曲，打破與蕾哈娜並列擁有最多冠軍單曲的紀錄。歌曲於榜單獲得非連續的五週冠軍位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-10-05/canadian-hot-100 |title=Canadian Hot 100 |work=Billboard |date=2013-10-05 |accessdate=2013-09-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131123042038/http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-10-05/canadian-hot-100 |archivedate=2013-11-23 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》亦獲得{{tsl|en|List of number-one digital songs of 2013 (Canada)||加拿大數位單曲榜}}非連續的三週冠軍位置，成為她於該榜的第6首冠軍單曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.musiccanada.com/Top20Digital.aspx?scid=65122 |title=Digital Tracks |work=Music Canada |publisher=Nielsen SoundScan Charts |date=2013-09-11 |accessdate=2013-09-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930015653/http://www.musiccanada.com/Top20Digital.aspx?scid=65122 |archivedate=2013-09-30 }}</ref>。在墨西哥，歌曲登上{{tsl|en|Monitor Latino||拉丁監控}}的英語歌曲電台榜冠軍位置<ref name="RadioNotas">{{cite web |url=http://monitorlatino.com.mx//Charts/Ingles93020131062013.html |work={{tsl|en|Monitor Latino||Monitor Latino}} |publisher=RadioNotas |accessdate=2013-10-06 |title=Top 20 Ingles: Del 30 de Septiembre al 6 de Octubre del 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015102611/http://monitorlatino.com.mx//Charts/Ingles93020131062013.html |archivedate=2013-10-15 }}</ref>。

