在英國，歌曲首週以179,500首下載量空降[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]冠軍位置，取代了[[埃利·古尔丁|埃利·古尔丁]]的《{{tsl|en|Burn (Ellie Goulding song)||燃燒}}》成為派瑞於當地第4首冠軍單曲<ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/katy-perry-roars-to-the-top-of-the-official-singles-chart-2475/ |title=Katy Perry Roars to the top of the Official Singles Chart |publisher=Officialcharts.com |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012014319/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/katy-perry-roars-to-the-top-of-the-official-singles-chart-2475/ |archivedate=2013-10-12 }}</ref>。歌曲於冠軍位置逗留了兩週，隨即被[[杰森·德鲁罗|杰森·德鲁罗]] （[[2_Chainz|雙鍊大師]]客串）的《{{tsl|en|Talk Dirty (Jason Derulo song)||咬耳朵}}》拉下冠軍位置。歌曲同時登上蘇格蘭單曲榜與[[爱尔兰单曲榜|爱尔兰单曲榜]]的冠軍位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2013&year=2013&week=34 |title=GFK Chart-Track |publisher=Chart-track.co.uk |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012011534/http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2013&year=2013&week=34 |archivedate=2013-10-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/22/2013-09-14/ |title=2013-09-14 Top 40 Scottish Singles Archive |publisher=Official Charts Company |date=2013-09-14 |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020021623/http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/22/2013-09-14 |archivedate=2013-10-20 }}</ref>。《聽我吼》於2013年終成為英國該年銷量第6高的單曲<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-singles-of-2013-2709/ |title=The Official Top 40 Biggest Selling Singles Of 2013 |publisher=[[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]] |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223235852/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-singles-of-2013__3658/ |archivedate=2015-02-23 |accessdate=2017-10-14 }}</ref>，並繼《煙火》後在2015年1月於當地突破100萬下載量，使派瑞成為第18名於當地擁有複數銷量突破百萬單曲的歌手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/katy-perry-super-bowl-half-time-show-roar-one-million-sales-3453/ |title=Katy Perry's Roar hits one million UK sales ahead of Super Bowl Half Time Show |last=Copsey |first=Rob |date=2015-01-31 |publisher=[[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=2015-01-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131151559/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/katy-perry-super-bowl-half-time-show-roar-one-million-sales-3453/ |archivedate=2015-01-31 }}</ref>。截至2017年，歌曲於英國售出1,112,787首<ref name="ukmillion2017">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-uks-official-chart-millionaires-revealed__20459/|publisher=Official Charts Company|date=2017-09-19|accessdate=2017-09-19|title=The UK's Official Chart 'millionaires' revealed|first=Rob|last=Copsey|archive-date=2017-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919122703/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-uks-official-chart-millionaires-revealed__20459/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並獲[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]認證為雙白金唱片<ref name="bpi"/>。

歌曲於[[意大利音乐产业联盟|意大利單曲榜]]最高達到第4位，並獲[[意大利音乐产业联盟|意大利音乐产业联盟]]認證為白金唱片，代表達到15,000首下載量<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fimi.it/archivio_certificazioni.php |title=FIMI - Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana - Certificazioni |publisher=Fimi.it |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006100124/http://www.fimi.it/archivio_certificazioni.php |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref>。在西班牙，單曲於[[西班牙音樂製作協會|西班牙音樂製作協會]]最高達到第5名<ref>{{cite web |author=Steffen Hung |url=http://www.spanishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |title=Katy Perry - Roar |publisher=spanishcharts.com |accessdate=2013-10-23 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617220555/https://spanishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在奧地利，歌曲登上[[奧地利Ö3四十強音樂榜|奧地利Ö3四十強音樂榜]]冠軍位置，亦分別登上德國與瑞士單曲榜的亞軍與季軍位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.de/song.asp?artist=Katy+Perry&title=Roar&cat=s&country=de |title=charts.de |publisher=charts.de |accessdate=2013-10-23 |archive-date=2014-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215092807/http://www.officialcharts.de/song.asp?artist=Katy+Perry&title=Roar&cat=s&country=de |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Steffen Hung |url=http://www.swisscharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |title=Katy Perry - Roar |publisher=swisscharts.com |accessdate=2013-10-23 |archive-date=2014-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126020936/http://swisscharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在比利時[[Ultratop榜|Ultratop榜]]，《聽我吼》分別於[[法兰德斯|法兰德斯]]與[[瓦隆大区|瓦隆大区]]登上最高第5位以及第7位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |title=Katy Perry - Roar |publisher=ultratop.be |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927200433/http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy%20Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |archivedate=2013-09-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |title=Katy Perry - Roar |publisher=ultratop.be |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014005724/http://www.ultratop.be/fr/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy%20Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |archivedate=2013-10-14 }}</ref>。歌曲於法國最高登上第6位<ref>{{cite web |author=Steffen Hung |url=http://www.lescharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |title=Katy Perry - Roar |publisher=lescharts.com |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929161601/http://lescharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy%20Perry&titel=Roar&cat=s |archivedate=2013-09-29 }}</ref>。歌曲於挪威最高登上第5位<ref name="Norwegian singles chart">{{cite web |url=http://lista.vg.no/liste/topp-20-single/1/dato/2013/uke/36 |title=Norwegian singles chart |date=2013-09-06 |accessdate=2013-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928011530/http://lista.vg.no/liste/topp-20-single/1/dato/2013/uke/36 |archivedate=2013-09-28 |df= }}</ref>。《聽我吼》亦登上捷克共和國、匈牙利與斯洛伐克電台榜的前10位。作為於當地的非官方數碼單曲榜，歌曲分別登上希臘與盧森堡的《告示牌》數碼單曲榜第2位，以及於葡萄牙的同一榜單登上第8位<ref name="billboard.com"/><ref name="ReferenceB">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/charts/2013-08-24/portugal |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |accessdate=2013-08-24 |title=Portugal Digital Songs - August 24, 2013 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305075002/http://www.billboard.com/biz/charts/2013-08-24/portugal |archivedate=2014-03-05 }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。

