高登|艾麗·高登]]、[[凱茜·馬斯格雷夫斯|凱茜·馬斯格雷夫斯]]以及組合[[泰根與莎拉|泰根與莎拉]]面前演唱了歌曲<ref name="Hollywood Bowl">{{cite web |last=Aguila |first=Justino |title=Katy Perry Hosts Famous Friends, Previews Next Tour at Hollywood Bowl: Live Review |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5770379/katy-perry-hosts-famous-friends-previews-next-tour-at-hollywood |work=Billboard |date=2013-10-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624200053/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5770379/katy-perry-hosts-famous-friends-previews-next-tour-at-hollywood |archivedate=2014-06-24 |accessdate=2017-10-16 }}</ref>。10月25日，派瑞於生日當天在美國萊克伍德高中舉行免費演唱會，演唱了《聽我吼》、《在空中漫步》其他3首經典歌曲，其中前3首歌曲於電視節目「[[早安美國|早安美國]]」現場直播<ref>{{cite web |title=Katy Perry at Lakewood High School: Students, faculty get private concert |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2013/10/25/katy-perry-at-lakewood-high-school-students-faculty-get-private-concert/ |publisher=The Denver Post Networld |author=Matt Miller |date=2013-10-25 |accessdate=2017-10-16 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617220805/https://www.denverpost.com/2013/10/25/katy-perry-at-lakewood-high-school-students-faculty-get-private-concert/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她亦於10月28日在澳洲版「[[X音素|X音素]]」上演唱了歌曲<ref name=XFactorPrismSongs>{{cite web |last=Kevipod |first=Kevin |title=Katy Perry Performs "Roar" & "Unconditionally" on "The X Factor Australia" |url=http://www.directlyrics.com/katy-perry-performs-roar-uncoditionally-on-the-x-factor-australia-news.html |publisher=directlyrics.com |accessdate=2013-10-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029205110/http://www.directlyrics.com/katy-perry-performs-roar-uncoditionally-on-the-x-factor-australia-news.html |archivedate=2013-10-29 }}</ref>，並在翌日於[[悉尼歌劇院|悉尼歌劇院]]表演了歌曲<ref>{{cite web |last=Somosot |first=Janice |title=Katy Perry 'Roars' at the Sydney Opera House for Aussie Promo of 'PRISM' Album |url=http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/518022/20131030/katy-perry-sydney-opera-house-prism-aussie.htm |website=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |publisher=IBT |accessdate=2014-12-17 |date=2013-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223185649/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/518022/20131030/katy-perry-sydney-opera-house-prism-aussie.htm |archivedate=2014-12-23 }}</ref>。11月16日，派瑞於德國電視節目「{{le|打敗拉布|Schlag den Raab}}」上演唱了歌曲<ref>{{cite web |title=Schlag den Raab 43 vom 16. November 2013 |url=http://www.prosieben.de/tv/schlag-den-raab/episodenguide/143-schlag-den-raab-43-vom-16-november-2013 |publisher=ProSiebenSat1 Networld |author=ProSieben |date=2013-11-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131117224608/http://www.prosieben.de/tv/schlag-den-raab/episodenguide/143-schlag-den-raab-43-vom-16-november-2013 |archivedate=2013-11-17 |accessdate=2017-10-16 }}</ref>。12月14日，派瑞在法國「[[NRJ音樂獎|NRJ音樂獎]]」上演唱歌曲，但於表演途中因技術問題而被主持上台請求重新演唱，這其後引起她於表演[[假唱|假唱]]的傳聞<ref>{{cite web |title=Katy Perry accused of lip-syncing "Roar" at NRJ Music Awards |url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/music/katy-perry-accused-of-lipsynching-roar-at-the-nrj-music-awards-in-france/story-e6frfn09-1226785867582 |publisher=News.com.au |accessdate=2014-01-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129003316/http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/music/katy-perry-accused-of-lipsynching-roar-at-the-nrj-music-awards-in-france/story-e6frfn09-1226785867582 |archivedate=2014-01-29 }}</ref>。頒獎禮一方其後向派瑞致歉，澄清她當時的確是在真唱，但因播放錯誤的歌曲混音以致蓋過她的現場歌聲，讓派瑞看起來像使用預先準備好的人聲假唱<ref name="nrj">{{cite web |url=http://nrjmusicawards.nrj.fr/nomines-4519/artiste/actu/561-katy-perry.html?actu_id=306298_katy-perry-remporte-le-nrj-music-award-du-best-digital-moment- |title=KATY PERRY REMPORTE LE NRJ MUSIC AWARD DU BEST DIGITAL MOMENT ! |language= |publisher=nrjmusicawards.nrj.fr |date=2013-12-15 |accessdate=2014-01-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113081742/http://nrjmusicawards.nrj.fr/nomines-4519/artiste/actu