2013年9月16日，[[辛辛那提孟加拉虎隊|辛辛那提孟加拉虎隊]]在「{{le|週一足球夜|Monday Night Football}}」與[[匹茲堡鋼人|匹茲堡鋼人隊]]的比賽上的介紹球員環節上，出乎意料地使用了《聽我吼》作為背景音樂，因歌曲的[[叢林|叢林]]主題與球隊的[[孟加拉虎|外號]]相似。歌曲其後亦偶爾在賽事休息的時間被播放。雖然最後隊伍以20比10的成績勝出賽事，但使用的歌曲遭到球隊的支持者甚至隊員本身的批評。其中一名球隊支持者更向《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》表示附近的鋼人隊支持者在嘲笑自己<ref name=steelers>{{Cite news| title = Steelers Turn To Power Of 'Renegade' To Fuel Defense: 'Oh Momma' Rallying Cry For Black And Gold| publisher = thepittsburghchannel.com| date = 2009-11-09| url = http://www.thepittsburghchannel.com/sports/21562637/detail.html| archivedate = 2009-11-23| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5lUNrH0FM?url=http://www.thepittsburghchannel.com/sports/21562637/detail.html| accessdate = 2017-10-16| dead-url = no}}</ref>。球隊於4天後作公開道歉，指歌曲雖然不會從{{le|保羅·布朗體育場|Paul Brown Stadium}}歌曲列表中剔出，但將會在介紹球員環節上使用[[硬式搖滾|硬式搖滾]]或{{le|經典搖滾|Classic rock}}歌曲<ref name=ESPN>{{cite web |title=Katy Perry song nixed for intros |url=http://espn.go.com/nfl/story/_/id/9701089/cincinnati-bengals-tone-katy-perry-roar-fan-backlash |publisher=ESPN |date=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231005020/http://espn.go.com/nfl/story/_/id/9701089/cincinnati-bengals-tone-katy-perry-roar-fan-backlash |archivedate=2013-12-31 |accessdate=2017-10-16 }}</ref>。2013年11月17日，歌曲在「[[吉列合唱團|吉列合唱團]]」播映的集數《{{le|凱蒂還是嗄嗄|A Katy or a Gaga}}》中被翻唱<ref>{{cite web |title='Glee' Episode 5.4 Songs: Lady Gaga's 'Applause' vs. Katy Perry's 'Roar' |url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/glee/glee-episode-54-songs-lady-gag-51765.aspx |author=Jeff Dodge |publisher=Buddy TV |date=2013-11-05 |accessdate=2017-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015135958/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/glee/glee-episode-54-songs-lady-gag-51765.aspx |archive-date=2017-10-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。歌曲亦被用於電影《[[老闆不是人2|老闆不是人2]]》與《[[海灘救護隊_(電影)|海灘救護隊]]》<ref>{{cite web |title=Horrible Bosses 2 (2014) Soundtracks |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2170439/soundtrack |publisher=[[互联网电影数据库|IMDb]] |accessdate=2017-10-16 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617220912/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2170439/soundtrack }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Baywatch (2017) Music Soundtracks - Complete Song List |url=https://www.tunefind.com/movie/baywatch-2017 |publisher=Tunefind |accessdate=2017-10-16 |archive-date=2021-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206033305/https://www.tunefind.com/movie/baywatch-2017 }}</ref>。混合武術家{{le|米莎·塔特|Miesha Tate}}亦在比賽時使用歌曲作為進場音樂<ref>{{cite web |title=Top five wackiest walkout songs in MMA |url=https://www.axs.com/top-five-wackiest-walkout-songs-in-mma-28257 |author=Eric Holden |publisher=AXS |date=2014-11-14 |accessdate=2017-10-16 |archive-date=2017-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171017042051/https://www.axs.com/top-five-wackiest-walkout-songs-in-mma-28257 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

